	(text_box "Board Description:\nProvided serial communications for end user: FTDI, UART, SPI, QSPI, I2C\nPower Input: From SCALES EPS Rev F (Hirose DF11 2x8 Connector)\nEthernet: 2, 10/100 Base-T RJ-45 Connectors\nSPI/GPIO/I2C: Provided via Hirose DF11 2x8 Connector\nSOM Connector: 2x140 proprietary Samtec Connector for IMX8QXP SOM"
